          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son is studying in grade 10 in SNP now. just right from his grade 9 the approach of the teachers is quite different than middle school. much of importance is given students with improving in their academic performances. all the teachers , co ordinators and HM and Principal mam focus on every single child for their better performance. regular class tests and monitoring helps children for their exam preparation.  not just with academics but also with external competitions children get plenty of opportunities to exhibit their life skills too like TED talks and various MUN's . thanks to the management.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
