            "name": "moni prabhakaran"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-03",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We are happy and fortunate that we find the best school for our kid (grade 4). Happy to be part of SNP family .\n\nHappy that they helping the kids in extra curricular too other than studies .\n\nTeachers and co-ordinators are kind enough to answer our queries.\n\nEverything get solvable when we meet them in person.\n\nGreat environment and facilities. This is the best among the localities.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
