          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Highly appreciated the activities taken by the teachers for Mother's day celebration and the day boarding staff for boosting my daughter confidence in other activities too.\n\nThanks to all the teachers for making the Mother's day celebration such a wonderful and memorable experience for all participants especially Mothers and kids.\n\nI like to take this privilege to congratulate the management of the School for its endless efforts and for your hard work in supporting my daughter (UKG PEARL Section) for this activity.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "SHREE NIKETAN PATASALA - VARADARA JAPURAM"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Dr Jayasree R"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-05-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school knows only to showcase their positives to attract new admissions each year. But actually, their is nothing worth in this school. Fees structure is increasing each year. Very money minded. No great teaching as teachers are constantly replaced several times within a academic year. You can never expect a polite conversation from anybody in the school, especially from any non-teaching staffs. Children will loose their character, discipline and respecting others by seeing the behaviour of these staffs only. Don't expect any individual attention to our child. You can't contact the teacher for any problem that needs to be addressed immediately. Only outstanding children will be given opportunities in any school events. Moderate and average students will never get any encouragement. Disappointed overall..",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
